下面给你一个可直接用的完整 CloudWatch Dashboard JSON 模板（已按你这个场景设计）：
👉 一个下拉 env
👉 env1 / env2 分别映射不同的 cluster + namespace
👉 同时包含 Logs + Metrics 示例
适用于 Amazon CloudWatch
✅ ✅ 完整 Dashboard JSON（可直接导入）
JSON
{
  "widgets": [
    {
      "type": "log",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 24,
      "height": 8,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Application Logs",
        "region": "ap-southeast-2",
        "query": "SOURCE '/aws/containerinsights/clusterA/application', '/aws/containerinsights/clusterB/application'\n| filter (\n    ('${env}' = 'env1' and kubernetes.cluster_name = 'clusterA' and kubernetes.namespace_name = 'nsA')\n    or\n    ('${env}' = 'env2' and kubernetes.cluster_name = 'clusterB' and kubernetes.namespace_name = 'nsB')\n)\n| fields @timestamp, kubernetes.pod_name, @message\n| sort @timestamp desc\n| limit 100"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 8,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Pod CPU Utilization",
        "region": "ap-southeast-2",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stat": "Average",
        "period": 300,
        "metrics": [
          [
            "ContainerInsights",
            "pod_cpu_utilization",
            "ClusterName",
            "clusterA",
            "Namespace",
            "nsA",
            { "id": "m1", "visible": false }
          ],
          [
            "ContainerInsights",
            "pod_cpu_utilization",
            "ClusterName",
            "clusterB",
            "Namespace",
            "nsB",
            { "id": "m2", "visible": false }
          ],
          [
            {
              "expression": "IF('${env}'='env1', m1, m2)",
              "label": "CPU Usage",
              "id": "e1"
            }
          ]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "metric",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 8,
      "width": 12,
      "height": 6,
      "properties": {
        "title": "Pod Memory Utilization",
        "region": "ap-southeast-2",
        "view": "timeSeries",
        "stat": "Average",
        "period": 300,
        "metrics": [
          [
            "ContainerInsights",
            "pod_memory_utilization",
            "ClusterName",
            "clusterA",
            "Namespace",
            "nsA",
            { "id": "m1", "visible": false }
          ],
          [
            "ContainerInsights",
            "pod_memory_utilization",
            "ClusterName",
            "clusterB",
            "Namespace",
            "nsB",
            { "id": "m2", "visible": false }
          ],
          [
            {
              "expression": "IF('${env}'='env1', m1, m2)",
              "label": "Memory Usage",
              "id": "e1"
            }
          ]
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variables": [
    {
      "type": "property",
      "id": "env",
      "label": "Environment",
      "inputType": "select",
      "visible": true,
      "values": [
        { "label": "Environment 1", "value": "env1" },
        { "label": "Environment 2", "value": "env2" }
      ],
      "defaultValue": "env1"
    }
  ]
}
🔧 你需要改的地方（很重要）
把这几项替换成你自己的：
1️⃣ Cluster 名
Plain text
clusterA → 你的 env1 cluster
clusterB → 你的 env2 cluster
2️⃣ Namespace
Plain text
nsA → env1 namespace
nsB → env2 namespace
3️⃣ Log Group（如果不一样）
默认是 Container Insights：
Plain text
/aws/containerinsights/<cluster>/application
如果你不是这个路径，要改：
SQL
SOURCE '你的log group'
✅ 最终效果
你会得到：
👉 Dashboard 顶部一个下拉框：
Environment 1
Environment 2
👉 切换后：
Logs 自动切 cluster + namespace
CPU / Memory 图自动切
⚠️ 关键理解（帮你避免后面踩坑）
CloudWatch 本质限制：
❌ 不能：
env → 自动拆成 cluster / namespace
✅ 只能：
手动在 query 里写映射（你现在这个方案）
